\boxed{**Gawain**}

Gawain is the most commonly cited survivor of the jentillak (a mythical race from Arthurian legend) after the Christian era, as referenced in medieval texts like *Sir Gawain and the Green Knight*. The jentillak were often depicted as noble, pre-Christian beings, and Gawain embodies their chivalric ideals. His survival symbolizes the blending of pagan and Christian traditions in Arthurian lore.
